@node getopt.h
@section @file{getopt.h}

Defines the type @code{struct option} and declares the variables
@code{optarg}, @code{optind}, @code{opterr}, @code{optopt}
and the functions @code{getopt}, @code{getopt_long}, @code{getopt_long_only}.

